'''東平壤競技場'''（{{kor|k=동평양경기장|hj=東平壤競技場|rm=Tong-P'yŏngyang gyŏnggijang}}）是[[朝鮮民主主義人民共和國|朝鮮民主主義人民共和國]]首都[[平壤|平壤]]的一座[[體育場|體育場]]。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://cafe.daum.net/stade/5BXH/66?docid=1DZEG5BXH6620110407124655 |title=세계의 주요 경기장 {{!}} Satellite Pictures of North Korean Stadiums - Daum 카페 |access-date=2015-01-11 |archive-date=2016-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305013703/http://cafe.daum.net/stade/5BXH/66?docid=1DZEG5BXH6620110407124655 |dead-url=no }}</ref>主要用作[[足球|足球]]比賽場地。它是在前領導人[[金日成|金日成]]的指導下，作為平壤市主要體育場館的補充而兴建。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://ndfsk.dyndns.org/kuguk8/munon84-24.htm |title=김 정 일  체육을 발전시킬데 대하여 |accessdate=2015-01-11 |archive-date=2015-01-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150111121952/http://ndfsk.dyndns.org/kuguk8/munon84-24.htm |dead-url=yes }}</ref>球場始建於1960年，場內可容納約3万<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.worldstadiums.com/asia/countries/north_korea.shtml |title=World Stadiums - Stadiums in North Korea |access-date=2015-01-11 |archive-date=2013-05-20 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6GkmApn1e?url=http://www.worldstadiums.com/asia/countries/north_korea.shtml |dead-url=yes }}</ref>至4万人。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://nk.joins.com/dic/view.asp?idx=20001227232143 |title=주요체육시설 |access-date=2015-01-11 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304120300/http://nk.joins.com/dic/view.asp?idx=20001227232143 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

